#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &systemsettings; provides the user with a centralized and convenient way "
"to configure all of the settings for your desktop."
msgstr ""
"&systemsettings; uporabniku ponuja centraliziran in priročen način za "
"konfiguriranje vseh nastavitev za vaše namizje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&systemsettings; is made up of multiple modules. Each module is a separate "
"application, however the &systemsettings; organizes all of these "
"applications into a single location."
msgstr ""
"&systemsettings; je sestavljen iz več modulov. Vsak modul je ločena "
"aplikacija, vendar &systemsettings; organizira vse te aplikacije na enem "
"mestu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each &systemsettings; module can be executed individually"
msgstr "Vsak &systemsettings; modul se lahko izvede posamično"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See section entitled <link linkend=\"run-modules-individually\">Running "
"individual &systemsettings; modules</link> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Glejte razdelek z naslovom <link linkend=\"run-modules-individually"
"\">Izvajanje posameznih &systemsettings; moduli</link> za več informacij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&systemsettings; groups all of the configuration modules into several "
"categories:"
msgstr "&systemsettings; združuje vse konfiguracijske module v več kategorij:"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"appearance\">Appearance</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"appearance\">Videz</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"workspace\">Workspace</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"workspace\">Delovni prostor</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"personalization\">Personalization</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"personalization\">Prilagajanje</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"network\">Network</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"network\">Omrežje</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"hardware\">Hardware</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"hardware\">Strojna oprema</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"system_administration\">System Administration</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"system administrator\">Sistemsko skrbništvo</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The modules that make up &systemsettings; fall under one of the above "
"categories, making it easier to locate the correct configuration module."
msgstr ""
"Moduli, ki sestavljajo &systemsettings; spadajo v eno od zgornjih kategorij, "
"kar olajša iskanje pravilnega konfiguracijskega modula."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &systemsettings;"
msgstr "Uporaba &systemsettings;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section details the use of &systemsettings; itself. For information on "
"each individual module, please see <link linkend=\"modules"
"\">&systemsettings; Modules</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek podrobno opisuje uporabo &systemsettings; sama. Za informacije o "
"vsakem posameznem modulu si oglejte <link linkend=\"modules"
"\">&systemsettings; Moduli</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &systemsettings;"
msgstr "Zagon &systemsettings;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &systemsettings; can be started in one of three ways:"
msgstr "&systemsettings; lahko začnete na enega od treh načinov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>System "
"Settings</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the <guilabel>Application Menu</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Z izbiro <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Sistemske "
"nastavitve</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v <guilabel>meniju aplikacij</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By pressing <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> or <keycombo>&Alt;"
"<keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo>. This will bring up the &krunner; dialog. "
"Type <command>systemsettings</command>, and press &Enter;."
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> ali <keycombo>&Alt;"
"<keycap>Preslednica</keycap></keycombo>. To bo prikazalo &krunner; dialog. "
"Vnesite <command>systemsettings</command> in pritisnite &Enter;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type <command>systemsettings &amp;</command> at any command prompt."
msgstr ""
"V poljuben ukazni poziv vnesite <command>systemsettings &amp;</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "All three of these methods are equivalent, and produce the same result."
msgstr "Vse te tri metode so enakovredne in dajejo enak rezultat."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &systemsettings; Screen"
msgstr "&systemsettings; zaslon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &systemsettings;, you are presented with a window, which is "
"divided into two functional parts."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete &systemsettings;, se vam prikaže okno, ki je razdeljeno na dva "
"funkcionalna dela."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Across the top is a toolbar. The toolbar provides the user with the ability "
"to go back into the main view from within a module using <guibutton>All "
"Settings</guibutton>. You can also find a <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu as "
"well as a <guibutton>Configure</guibutton> button which provides you a "
"dialog with alternate view settings."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu je orodna vrstica. Orodna vrstica omogoča uporabniku, da se vrne v "
"glavni pogled znotraj modula z uporabo <guibutton>Vse nastavitve</"
"guibutton>. Najdete lahko tudi meni <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> in gumb "
"<guibutton>Konfiguriraj</guibutton>, ki vam ponudi pogovorno okno z "
"alternativnimi nastavitvami pogleda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To search for something within all of the modules, start to type keywords "
"into the search field at the right of the toolbar in the <guibutton>All "
"Settings</guibutton> view. When you start typing, a list of matching topics "
"will popup. Select one and only the groups with settings for this keyword "
"are enabled, the other are greyed out."
msgstr ""
"Če želite poiskati nekaj znotraj vseh modulov, začnite vnašati ključne "
"besede v iskalno polje na desni strani orodne vrstice v pogledu "
"<guibutton>Vse nastavitve</guibutton>. Ko začnete tipkati, se prikaže seznam "
"ujemajočih se tem. Izberite eno in omogočene bodo samo skupine z "
"nastavitvami za to ključno besedo, druge so zatemnjene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the icon window has the focus, you can type the first letter of any "
"module or module group name to select it. Typing this letter again the "
"selection moves to the next match."
msgstr ""
"Ko je okno z ikonami v fokusu, lahko vnesete prvo črko imena katerega koli "
"modula ali skupine modulov, da ga izberete. Če ponovno vnesete to črko, se "
"izbor premakne na naslednje ujemanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Underneath the toolbar is an icon view of the individual modules or module "
"groups that make up &systemsettings; grouped by different categories. By "
"default, if your mouse stays a few seconds over an icon, a tooltip appears, "
"either explaining the purpose of the module or showing the modules in this "
"group."
msgstr ""
"Pod orodno vrstico je pogled ikon posameznih modulov ali skupin modulov, ki "
"sestavljajo &systemsettings; razvrščeni po različnih kategorijah. Če se "
"miška nekaj sekund zadrži nad ikono, se privzeto prikaže opis orodja, ki "
"pojasnjuje namen modula ali prikazuje module v tej skupini."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "&systemsettings; Categories and Modules"
msgstr "&systemsettings; Kategorije in moduli"

#. Tag: para
