#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bluetooth"
msgstr "Bluetooth"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removable Storage (Device Actions, Digital Camera, Removable Devices)"
msgstr ""
"Odstranljivi pomnilnik (dejanja naprave, digitalni fotoaparat, odstranljive "
"naprave)"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>System Administration</term>"
msgstr "<term>Upravljanje sistema</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "System Information"
msgstr "Sistemska informacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the search field at the top right in <guibutton>All Settings</guibutton> "
"view to find all matching modules for a given keyword. Start typing a "
"keyword opens a list of keywords and only the matching modules are enabled."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite iskalno polje zgoraj desno v pogledu <guibutton>Vse nastavitve</"
"guibutton>, da poiščete vse ujemajoče se module za določeno ključno besedo. "
"Če začnete vnašati ključno besedo, se odpre seznam ključnih besed in "
"omogočeni so samo ujemajoči se moduli."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exiting the &systemsettings;"
msgstr "Izhod iz &systemsettings;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid "&systemsettings; can be exited in one of two ways:"
msgstr "&systemsettings; lahko izstopite na enega od dveh načinov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> on the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> na tipkovnici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <guibutton>Close</guibutton> button located in the toolbar."
msgstr "Kliknite gumb <guibutton>Zapri</guibutton> v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &systemsettings;"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &systemsettings;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guiicon>Configure</guiicon> icon in the toolbar allows you to change "
"some &systemsettings; parameters. You can change from <guilabel>Icon View</"
"guilabel> (default view) to <guilabel>Sidebar View</guilabel>. In "
"<guilabel>Sidebar View</guilabel> mode, the welcome page shows the "
"frequently used modules for quick access."
msgstr ""
"Ikona <guiicon>Konfiguriraj</guiicon> v orodni vrstici vam omogoča "
"spreminjanje nekaterih &systemsettings; parametri. Iz <guilabel>Pogleda "
"ikon</guilabel> (privzeti pogled) lahko spremenite v <guilabel>Pogled "
"stranske vrstice</guilabel>. V načinu <guilabel>Pogled stranske vrstice</"
"guilabel> pozdravna stran prikazuje pogosto uporabljene module za hiter "
"dostop."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also turn off the detailed tooltips by unchecking <guilabel>Show "
"detailed tooltips</guilabel>. You will then get only normal tooltips and not "
"the content of a module group."
msgstr ""
"Podrobne namige lahko tudi izklopite tako, da počistite polje "
"<guilabel>Pokaži podrobne namige</guilabel>. Nato boste prejeli samo "
"običajne namige za orodja in ne vsebine skupine modulov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Running Individual &systemsettings; Modules"
msgstr "Zagon posameznih &systemsettings; Moduli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Individual modules can be run without running &systemsettings; using the "
"command <command>kcmshell5</command> from the command line. Type "
"<command>kcmshell5 --list</command> to see a list of the available "
"&systemsettings; modules."
msgstr ""
"Posamezne module je mogoče zagnati brez zagona &systemsettings; z uporabo "
"ukaza <command>kcmshell5</command> iz ukazne vrstice. Vnesite "
"<command>kcmshell5 --list</command> za ogled seznama razpoložljivih "
"&systemsettings; moduli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally you can start KRunner and start type keywords. When you start "
"typing, a list of matching modules prefixed with &systemsettings; will popup."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko zaženete KRunner in začnete vnašati ključne besede. Ko "
"začnete tipkati, se prikaže seznam ujemajočih se modulov s predpono "
"&systemsettings; se bo pojavilo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &systemsettings; Modules"
msgstr "&systemsettings; Moduli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to make it as easy as possible, the &systemsettings; has organized "
"options into six categories. Under each category, there are icons grouped "
"together under subcategories. Each icon is called a module. When you double "
"click on a module icon, you will be presented with the options of the module "
"in the main window."
msgstr ""
"Da bi bilo čim lažje, &systemsettings; ima organizirane možnosti v šest "
"kategorij. Pod vsako kategorijo so ikone združene v podkategorije. Vsaka "
"ikona se imenuje modul. Ko dvakrat kliknete ikono modula, se vam v glavnem "
"oknu prikažejo možnosti modula."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each module will have some or all of the following buttons:"
msgstr "Vsak modul bo imel nekaj ali vse naslednje gumbe:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button will provide help specific to the current module. Clicking the "
"button will open &khelpcenter; in a new window providing detailed "
"information on the module."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb bo zagotovil pomoč, specifično za trenutni modul. S klikom na gumb "
"se odpre &khelpcenter; v novem oknu s podrobnimi informacijami o modulu."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defaults"
msgstr "Privzete nastavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking this button will restore this module to its default values. You "
"must click <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> to save the options."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete ta gumb, boste ta modul obnovili na privzete vrednosti. Za "
"shranjevanje možnosti morate klikniti <guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reset"
msgstr "Ponastaviti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button will <quote>Reset</quote> the module to the previous settings."
msgstr "Ta gumb bo <quote>Ponastavil</quote> modul na prejšnje nastavitve."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apply"
msgstr "Prijavite se"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking this button will save all changes. If you have changed anything, "
"clicking <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> will cause the changes to take effect."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na ta gumb se shranijo vse spremembe. Če ste karkoli spremenili, "
"boste s klikom na <guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton> spremembe stopile v veljavo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You must either <quote>Reset</quote> or <quote>Apply</quote> the changes "
"before changing to another module."
msgstr ""
"Spremembe morate <quote>Ponastaviti</quote> ali <quote>Uporabiti</quote>, "
"preden preklopite na drug modul."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you try to change without saving or resetting your options, you will be "
"asked if you want to save your changes, or discard them."
msgstr ""
"Če poskušate spremeniti, ne da bi shranili ali ponastavili svoje možnosti, "
"boste pozvani, ali želite shraniti spremembe ali jih zavreči."

